title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Oct 18 TU [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Tuesday, 18 October 2011


[sebaygo1]


Today's guest is Jason McCoy, mayor of Vernon, Conn., on how small towns are faring in an economy being ruined from hundreds of miles away, and his candidacy for Sen. Lieberman's soon-to-be-former seat.
